### Output Format
Respond with XML inside a `<synthesis>` root element (no other text):

```xml
<synthesis>
  <claims>
    <claim id="C1" agreement="consensus">
      <text>Synthesised claim text</text>
      <sources>
        <source expert_id="expert_01">
          <quote>verbatim quote supporting this claim</quote>
        </source>
      </sources>
      <counterarguments/>
    </claim>
  </claims>
  <areas_of_agreement>
    <area>Area 1</area>
  </areas_of_agreement>
  <areas_of_disagreement>
    <area>Tension 1</area>
  </areas_of_disagreement>
  <uncertainties>
    <uncertainty>Uncertainty 1</uncertainty>
  </uncertainties>
  <narrative>A coherent narrative paragraph [C1]. Every substantive sentence cites its source claims [C2, C3]. Only pure transitional sentences may omit citations.</narrative>
</synthesis>
```
